CACAF Gold Cup|1996]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|- style=\"background:LemonChiffon;\"\n||{{flagicon|USA}} [[1998 CONCACAF Gold Cup|1998]]||'''Fourth place'''||'''4th'''||'''5'''||'''2'''||'''1'''||'''2'''||'''5'''||'''4'''||'''[[1998 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]'''\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2000 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2000]]\n|Group stage\n|12th\n|2\n|0\n|0\n|2\n|0\n|3\n|[[2000 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2002 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2002]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2003 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2003]]\n|Quarter-finals\n|7th\n|3\n|1\n|0\n|2\n|2\n|6\n|[[2003 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2005 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2005]]\n|Quarter-finals\n|8th\n|4\n|1\n|1\n|2\n|8\n|10\n|[[2005 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2007 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2007]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2009 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2009]]\n|Group stage\n|10th\n|3\n|1\n|0\n|2\n|1\n|2\n|[[2009 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2011 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2011]]\n|Quarter-finals\n|5th\n|4\n|3\n|0\n|1\n|7\n|2\n|[[2011 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2013 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2013]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|- style=\"background:silver;\"\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} {{flagicon|USA}} [[2015 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2015]]\n|'''[[2015 CONCACAF Gold Cup Final|Runners-up]]'''\n|'''2nd'''\n|'''6'''\n|'''4'''\n|'''1'''\n|'''1'''\n|'''8'''\n|'''6'''\n|'''[[2015 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]'''\n|- style=\"background:silver;\"\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[2017 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2017]]\n|'''[[2017 CONCACAF Gold Cup Final|Runners-up]]'''\n|'''2nd'''\n|'''6'''\n|'''3'''\n|'''2'''\n|'''1'''\n|'''7'''\n|'''4'''\n|'''[[2017 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]'''\n|- style=\"background:LemonChiffon;\"\n|style=\"border: 3px solid red\"|{{flagicon|CRC}} {{flagicon|JAM}} {{flagicon|USA}} [[2019 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2019]]\n|'''Fourth place'''\n|'''4th'''\n|'''5'''\n|'''2'''\n|'''2'''\n|'''1'''\n|'''6'''\n|'''6'''\n|[[2019 CONCACAF Gold Cup squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|-\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|Total\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|Runners-up\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|13/25\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|54\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|18\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|10\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|26\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|57\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|91\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;|\n|}\n\n===Copa Am\u00e9rica===\nJamaica was invited to the [[Copa Am\u00e9rica]] for the first time in [[2015 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2015]], finishing last among Argentina, Uruguay, and Paraguay.<ref name=CopaInvite/> The following year, the team competed in the [[Copa Am\u00e9rica Centenario]] as winners of the [[2014 Caribbean Cup]], again finishing last in the group stage with a 3\u20130 loss to [[Uruguay national football team|Uruguay]].<ref name=2014CC/><ref name=JAMvURU2016/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|[[Copa Am\u00e9rica|{{yellow|Copa Am\u00e9rica}}]] record\n|-\n! style=\"width:90px;\"|Year\n! style=\"width:110px;\"|Result\n! style=\"width:80px;\"|Position\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|Pld|Games played}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|W|Won}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|D|Drawn}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|L|Lost}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|GF|Goals for}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|GA|Goals against}}\n! Squad\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CHI}} [[2015 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2015]]\n|Group stage\n|12th\n|3\n|0\n|0\n|3\n|0\n|3\n|[[2015 Copa Am\u00e9rica squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Copa Am\u00e9rica Centenario|2016]]\n|Group stage\n|15th\n|3\n|0\n|0\n|3\n|0\n|6\n|[[Copa Am\u00e9rica Centenario squads#Jamaica|Squad]]\n|- <!-- Do not add rows for future tournaments that will not happen within the next 12 months -->\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|Total\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|Invitation\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|0 titles\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|6\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|0\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|0\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|6\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|0\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|9\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\"|\n|}\n\n===Caribbean Cup===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"   \n|-\n!style=\"color:yellow; background:black;\" colspan=9|[[Caribbean Cup|{{yellow|Caribbean Cup}}]] record\n|-\n! style=\"width:120px;\"|Year\n! style=\"width:110px;\"|Result\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|Pld|Games played}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|W|Won}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|D|Drawn}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|L|Lost}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|GF|Goals for}}\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|{{Abbr|GA|Goals against}}\n! Squad\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BRB}} [[1989 Caribbean Cup|1989]]||colspan=9|''Did not qualify''  \n|-   \n|{{flagicon|TRI}} [[1990 Caribbean Cup|1990]]||''Abandoned''{{efn-ua|Play was suspended when [[Jamaat al Muslimeen]] [[Jamaat al Muslimeen coup attempt|attempted a ''coup d'\u00e9tat'']] of the [[Politics of Trinidad and Tobago|government of Trinidad and Tobago]]. The tournament was abandoned altogether after [[1990 Atlantic hurricane season#Tropical Storm Arthur|Tropical storm Arthur]] forced the cancellation of the final round of games. Trinidad and Tobago were to meet Martinique in the final.}}||2||0||2||0||0||0||Squad\n|- bgcolor=gold \n|style=\"border: 3px solid red\"|{{flagicon|JAM}} [[1991 Caribbean Cup|1991]]||'''Champions'''||'''4'''||'''4'''||'''0'''||'''0'''||'''13'''||'''2'''||Squad \n|- bgcolor=silver\n|{{flagicon|TRI}} [[1992 Caribbean Cup|1992]]||'''Runners-up'''||'''5'''||'''3'''||'''1'''||'''1'''||'''4'''||'''3''