um)|Alive]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"When It Comes to You\"<br>{{small|([[Adam F]] and Cory Enemy featuring Dizzee Rascal and Margot)}}\n| 2014\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[How Love Begins]]\"<br>{{small|([[DJ Fresh]] and [[High Contrast]] featuring Dizzee Rascal)}}\n| 2016\n| 53 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Blessed\"<br>{{small|([[Ocean Wisdom]] featuring Dizzee Rascal)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/blessed-feat-dizzee-rascal-single/1475477854|title=Blessed (feat. Dizzee Rascal) - Single by Ocean Wisdom|website=iTunes|accessdate=20 August 2019}}</ref>\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Big Talk, Vol. 1''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Back It\"<br>{{small|([[Yizzy]] featuring Dizzee Rascal)}}\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{TBA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Smoke\"<br>{{small|(Big Tobz featuring Dizzee Rascal)}}\n| 2020\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n| colspan=\"16\" style=\"font-size:90%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|-\n|}\n\n===Charity releases===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\" border=\"1\"\n|+ List of singles, with selected chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:27em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=UK/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Irish Singles Chart|IRE]]<br/><ref name=IRE/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2